   <titleInfo>
      <title>[Letter] 1845 Dec. 18, Nashville [Tennessee] [to] A. Fergusson, Carthage [Tennessee] / Sam Golluday</title>
   </titleInfo>
   <abstract>This is a letter from Sam Golluday to Adam Fergusson, dated December 18, 1845. Golluday has some coffee that Fergusson purchased. He also writes that he will soon be back in business, and looks forward to having Fergusson as a client.</abstract>
